      "text": "One app registration (proxy api://<proxy-app>): delegated Graph (User.Read) + SharePoint (AllSites.Read, User.Read.All)\n+ Azure ML user_impersonation. The proxy performs every OBO; the agent never sees the user's token. search_faq runs\nunder the agent's own identity (Managed Identity + Search Index Data Reader). Profile resolved/injected on the first turn only.",
